%% Tempo real: webhook → evento interno → WebSocket → cliente (Português)
sequenceDiagram
  participant NP as NowPayments
  participant API as API Pigbit
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant Bus as EventEmitter
  participant WS as Gateway /realtime
  participant Front as Frontend Checkout

  NP->>API: POST /webhooks/nowpayments
  API->>API: verifyWebhookSignature
  API->>DB: update fatura.status (pedido/carrinho)
  API->>Bus: emit invoice.status.updated
  Bus->>WS: OnEvent
  WS->>Front: invoiceStatus { paymentId, status }
  Note over Front: UI atualiza sem polling — feedback em tempo real
